Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.21,0:00:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.50,0:00:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.13,0:00:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.97,0:00:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我好害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.45,0:00:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不要一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.97,0:00:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你还在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.30,0:00:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司还在我的身边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.84,0:00:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 我在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.45,0:00:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我就在这
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.19,0:00:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哪里都不要去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.31,0:00:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.12,0:00:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我开动啰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.90,0:00:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.00,0:01:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}会不会觉得我做得比以前好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.60,0:01:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这是每天积累的成果呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.56,0:01:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我可是认真做就能做好的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.37,0:01:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.23,0:01:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.84,0:01:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}味道怎么样
Comment: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.14,0:03:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.72,0:03:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喂喂 司
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.49,0:03:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你现在是不是非常的想要去看电影呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.05,0:03:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你是这样想的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.63,0:03:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.70,0:03:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以把这个拿好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.88,0:03:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.52,0:03:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是为什么突然给我这个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.37,0:03:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}塞克很少会给我礼物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.42,0:03:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这是因为啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.59,0:03:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}满来拜托我帮她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.90,0:03:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以我才
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.33,0:03:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.30,0:03:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好啦你给我收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.41,0:03:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}跟艾拉两个人去开心一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.98,0:03:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.89,0:03:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}话先说在前头
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.96,0:03:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我只是很偶然地拿到了票
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.56,0:03:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是我可是很忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.45,0:03:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只好把票让给很闲的你们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.73,0:03:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真的只是这样哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.28,0:03:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.21,0:04:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}总之谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.32,0:04:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}噢 司君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.38,0:04:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}正好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.93,0:04:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这些你不介意的话就收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.09,0:04:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.99,0:04:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.09,0:04:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}游览地旅馆的目录
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.18,0:04:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要好好地利用哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.68,0:04:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.82,0:04:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我拿到了平时常去的饭店的招待券
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.47,0:04:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}让给你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.82,0:04:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}店里有着装规定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.33,0:04:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以我替你们准备了正装
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.76,0:04:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这是餐时表演的票和加油用品
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.51,0:04:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}粉丝俱乐部的特典里多放了两份
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.39,0:04:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}愿意的话就拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.51,0:04:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我的车
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.02,0:04:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你随时都可以开走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.60,0:04:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}停车场的地址在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.96,0:04:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什么 你没有驾照
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.59,0:04:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没事没事有自动驾驶功能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.98,0:04:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}抱歉呢 司君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.18,0:04:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我每个月的零用钱都好紧张的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.07,0:04:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以我只能给你这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.60,0:05:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}呃 机会难得 明天要休个假一起去逛逛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.39,0:05:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是像梦一般的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.07,0:05:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这不是梦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.44,0:05:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.88,0:05:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}多亏了你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.39,0:05:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}满足了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.75,0:05:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.62,0:05:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想做的事还有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.73,0:05:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好奇心真强烈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.50,0:05:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好羡慕你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.37,0:05:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}激情退却了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.88,0:05:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要好好的体验人生才好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.48,0:05:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不然就太浪费了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.27,0:05:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我只要能够独占你动人的笑容就好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.95,0:05:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只要这样我就满足了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.77,0:05:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.31,0:05:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}第一次看电影觉得怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.88,0:05:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}非常开心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.82,0:05:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}到现在还不能平静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.74,0:06:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刚才一直握着我的手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.81,0:06:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那是因为在黑暗的地方就担心司会不会忽然不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.27,0:06:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}感到很不安…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.59,0:06:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.07,0:06:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}给你添麻烦了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.29,0:06:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没有那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.19,0:06:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我的手你再怎么握都没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.74,0:06:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吶 司 我想试试电影里的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.56,0:06:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.32,0:06:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}难道是膝枕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.86,0:06:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我的膝盖可以用的…所以
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.49,0:06:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那…那就不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.01,0:06:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司的头发有点刺人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.95,0:06:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}超级害羞就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.70,0:06:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}错误 没有听清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.46,0:07:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 错误什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.07,0:07:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}其实是听清楚的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.27,0:07:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我没听到哟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.78,0:07:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.24,0:07:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吶 司
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.84,0:07:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我最近害怕晚上睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.29,0:07:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我会去想象
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.70,0:07:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}会不会再也醒不来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.55,0:07:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}会不会再也见不到司了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.62,0:07:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是像这样和司在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.78,0:07:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那种感觉就咻的消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.60,0:07:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司好厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.90,0:07:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你可以随时来依靠我的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.56,0:07:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.62,0:07:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明天怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.21,0:08:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}从大家那里感觉到超级强的「明天休息吧」的气场
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.39,0:08:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司想要去玩的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.62,0:08:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.15,0:08:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}表情很困扰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.91,0:08:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}虽然这样的每一天都很快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.10,0:08:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是这样下去身体会迟钝的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.56,0:08:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果…在迎接最后一天之前就不能动了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.37,0:08:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就好讨厌了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.45,0:08:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.54,0:08:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 不可能有那种事的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.39,0:08:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不过 一不小心就开始胡思乱想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.04,0:09:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那样的话…果然还是像平常那样度过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.51,0:09:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天这样的日子偶尔过一过就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.65,0:09:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谢谢
Comment: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.20,0:09:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}数据上没有什么显眼的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.47,0:09:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.31,0:09:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对不起我迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.26,0:09:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}太慢了 迟到10分钟了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.51,0:09:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}工作太忙了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.30,0:09:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.65,0:09:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}去准备
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.92,0:09:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我去换衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.03,0:09:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.70,0:09:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉的数据
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.99,0:09:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}难道今天也来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.70,0:09:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.11,0:09:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是的 那俩人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.15,0:09:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没有必要这么频繁的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.29,0:09:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也好 对本人来说能安抚一下情绪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.45,0:10:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这个我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.98,0:10:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就算如此 也没必要休息日也过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.81,0:10:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我看到他们两个人就想哭了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.73,0:10:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司 过来一下好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.00,0:10:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}正好我也有事情想问香月姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.92,0:10:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.95,0:10:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}希望你把下一个工作交给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.50,0:10:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我和艾拉负责的变成只有莎拉小姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.87,0:10:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什… 这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.05,0:10:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉的回收同意书
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.19,0:10:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}由你来签名
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.38,0:10:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.99,0:10:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你暂时集中关注艾拉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.46,0:11:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.78,0:11:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}德国洋甘菊是一年生的草本
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.90,0:11:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一直长着叶子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.70,0:11:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.87,0:11:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}种子落下来同时会长出新的芽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.88,0:11:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}放置不管的话会长一大片
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.94,0:11:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有不好的 最好是摘下来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.98,0:11:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.88,0:11:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这边的百里香怕热小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.74,0:11:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}反过来迷迭香很耐热
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.73,0:11:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是如果不整理的话叶子会太繁茂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.24,0:11:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}下面会枯掉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.27,0:11:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}夏天应该收获一次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.95,0:11:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.21,0:11:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.79,0:11:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉很了解药草呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.72,0:11:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}研究了很久吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.27,0:11:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刚开始培育的时候有很多时间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.78,0:11:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而且只要大家说我泡的茶好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.16,0:11:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我就觉得我能在这里待着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.02,0:12:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还想种些别的看看呢
Comment: 0,0:12:01.93,0:12:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.06,0:12:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.31,0:12:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.23,0:12:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.37,0:12:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊…不对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.78,0:12:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你这货在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.38,0:12:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因为现在只有我和艾拉的工作很轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.21,0:12:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就想着有没有什么其他可做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.69,0:12:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就让艾拉教我这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.51,0:12:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}最近好像找到窍门了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.81,0:12:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.88,0:12:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}「找到窍门了」个头啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.62,0:13:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以我才受不了外行人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.28,0:13:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}正好趁这个机会跟你说明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.86,0:13:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为什么不去休息啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.69,0:13:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你倒是稍微看一下气氛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.11,0:13:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.15,0:13:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}「咦」个头啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.94,0:13:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}比起来公司上班 你应该多花些时间来陪艾拉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.05,0:13:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就算你们不来上班大家也不会抱怨的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.78,0:13:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们不能休息啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.29,0:13:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.62,0:13:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}虽然满和大家说的 我们很感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.62,0:13:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但我和艾拉两个人做出了决定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.23,0:13:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就和平常一样就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.16,0:13:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我希望大家能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.66,0:13:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}满 是你输了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.71,0:13:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}香月姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.31,0:13:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你也是对他们一直放心不下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.87,0:13:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.36,0:13:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谢谢你 满
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.82,0:14:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.52,0:14:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是我也想象珍惜和司的时间一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.13,0:14:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}珍惜在这里度过的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.81,0:14:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}算了 随便你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.46,0:14:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好了 你们也别看了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.32,0:14:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}快回去工作 别偷懒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.02,0:14:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哎呀 待会还有约会要去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.56,0:14:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.10,0:14:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小艾拉 能再帮我倒杯茶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.55,0:14:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好的 马上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.68,0:14:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉 现在有空吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.22,0:14:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这个的签名 由我来签
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.17,0:14:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.05,0:14:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.36,0:14:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.90,0:14:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.72,0:14:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我希望司来签
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.04,0:14:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.12,0:15:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我的脑中有时会闪现出一些想法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.36,0:15:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们就这样逃到远方会怎样之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.16,0:15:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我就在想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.12,0:15:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}该怎样不告诉任何人然后离开
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.61,0:15:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}给你留下了痛苦的回忆了呢
Comment: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}水柿司
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.94,0:16:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.93,0:16:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明天就是莎拉小姐的回收日了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.03,0:16:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们两个负责的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.26,0:16:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这就是最后一件了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.19,0:16:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.17,0:16:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.43,0:16:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}是的 您说的我都明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.37,0:16:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}但是让我们什么都不做的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.56,0:16:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那…我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.58,0:16:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}也未免太说不过去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.02,0:16:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}是是 那个…那个…咦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.36,0:16:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那两个人已经走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.30,0:16:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}请您通融一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.38,0:16:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.44,0:16:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那我们开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.40,0:17:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.69,0:17:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}结束了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.34,0:17:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还没有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.90,0:17:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还剩下一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.46,0:17:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.52,0:17:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.95,0:17:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\fad(320,50)\c&H49465B&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(649,263)}有一件讯息
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.52,0:17:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.77,0:17:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}莎拉小姐的回收已经完成了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.96,0:17:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果有兴趣的话就回办公室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.61,0:17:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你们的工作也就全部告一段落了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.71,0:18:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们准备为你们开个小小的慰问会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.06,0:18:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}当然也不用勉强非要来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.37,0:18:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不管怎样先优先处理你们自己的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.42,0:18:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就算你们不来 我们也会HIGH起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.32,0:18:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.76,0:18:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再见
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.64,0:18:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}虽然这样说了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.56,0:18:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.22,0:18:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.57,0:18:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.80,0:18:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}欢迎回来～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.21,0:18:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}欢迎～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.09,0:18:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}回来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.61,0:18:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.73,0:18:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们已经开始了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.00,0:18:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.95,0:18:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天的主角出现啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.82,0:18:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在公司里喝酒真的没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.55,0:18:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没事 没事～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.71,0:18:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在这里的全员都已经把工作提前完成啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.25,0:18:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}虽然康孝你好像只是睡了一天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.87,0:19:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.64,0:19:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为了腾出今天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.57,0:19:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大家可是拚命提前完成了工作的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.70,0:19:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为此大家上周都过得非常忙碌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.90,0:19:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不管怎么说 现在已经是非工作时间啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.72,0:19:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我允许你们饮酒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.26,0:19:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不不 这是我允许的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.32,0:19:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我可是为了得到许可 卑躬屈膝地求了部长好久
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.95,0:19:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要老命了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.96,0:19:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}知道了 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.96,0:19:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你做的很好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.49,0:19:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来 两位请拿好这个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.85,0:19:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好的 全员注意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.11,0:19:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.26,0:19:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这么长时间以来 辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.80,0:19:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那么 干杯啰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:49.50,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\an9\bord0\fs20\c&H393939&\pos(251,142)\fsp0}香月就交给我吧。\N\N康斯坦斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:49.50,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\fsp0\an9\bord0\fs20\c&H393939&\pos(337,335)}辛苦了。暂时忘掉工作，\N先考虑自己的幸福吧，好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:49.50,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\fsp0\an9\bord0\fs20\c&H393939&\pos(320,443)}啊，不介意的话，什么时候\N来我房间里玩都可以哟？\N满
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:49.50,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\fsp0\an9\bord0\fs20\c&H393939&\pos(460,570)}谢谢你总是泡茶给我们。\N非常好喝唷。\N山野边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:49.50,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\fsp0\an9\bord0\fs20\c&H393939&\pos(298,667)}再见啰～\N塞克
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:49.50,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\fsp0\an9\bord0\fs30\c&H393939&\pos(711,137)}辛苦啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:49.50,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\fsp0\an9\bord0\fs20\c&H393939&\pos(877,142)}害羞了（笑）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:49.50,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\fsp0\an9\fs30\c&H393939&\3c&HFAFCFC&\pos(782,433)}艾拉 辛苦啦~！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:49.50,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\fsp0\an7\bord0\fs20\c&H393939&\pos(701,600)}艾拉酱LOVE\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h海松绘瑠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:49.50,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\fsp0\an9\bord0\fs20\c&H393939&\pos(1222,201)}第一终端服务课的友情永远不灭！\N土器连
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:49.50,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\fsp0\an9\bord0\fs20\c&H393939&\pos(1250,341)}从现在开始尽情对喜欢的男生撒娇吧。\N那样的任性会被允许的。\N康孝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:49.50,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\fsp0\an9\bord0\fs20\c&H393939&\pos(1235,470)}与你一起共事是非常值得骄傲的一件事。\N雪莉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:49.50,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\fsp0\an9\bord0\fs20\c&H393939&\pos(1238,615)}单元测验房会一直为你保留着的。\N右次郎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.67,0:19:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.69,0:20:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嘿～嘿～加油～加油～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.80,0:20:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嘿～嘿～加油～加油～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.91,0:20:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谢谢大家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.94,0:20:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉好像很开心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.21,0:20:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没想到你们真的回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.14,0:20:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}发来信息的就是满吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.52,0:20:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}虽然是那样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.24,0:20:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}虽然嘴上这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.13,0:20:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}说要开这个会的就是满啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.25,0:20:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}塞克
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.22,0:20:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是的 为什么每次都要戳穿我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.29,0:20:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.73,0:20:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}来 接着喝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.49,0:20:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没什么啊 反正我早就知道司是个需要别人照顾的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.35,0:20:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你笑什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.26,0:21:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你才是在笑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.18,0:21:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我才没在笑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.37,0:21:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}笑啦 笑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.63,0:21:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}塞克你也这样
Comment: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.45,0:21:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}累了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.93,0:21:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 好像有一点闹过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.26,0:21:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.14,0:21:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没事啦 没事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.88,0:21:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}开心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.47,0:21:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我觉得 虽然发生了许多事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.38,0:21:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是能在那里工作真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.83,0:21:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.98,0:21:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}能遇到大家 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.48,0:21:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.64,0:21:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}现在开心的 愉快的事太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.95,0:21:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}多到日记里都写不下了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.66,0:21:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这些都是托司的福
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.12,0:21:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.71,0:21:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我可以问个问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.29,0:21:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.29,0:21:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天你对莎拉小姐说了些什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.95,0:21:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.06,0:22:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}之前 每次回收的最后你都一定会那样做
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.62,0:22:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我之前就很在意了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.79,0:22:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}会想你都说了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.36,0:22:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}「愿你终将与重要的人再次相会」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
